To build Cgc (Coin Graph Classes), see the INSTALL file.

To use Cgc you do not need any other packgaes or libraries.  

Cgc is a template header library.  The code is compiled into 
your executable when you build your executable.

To see an example use of Cgc, see the examples directory.  
To build an example:
cd examples
make 

To build the unit tests:
cd test
make 

